The blessed giant rat is a type of giant rat on the second floor in the Underground Pass.

Due to its 30 Hitpoints and low Defence, the blessed giant rat can be good for training Combat on at low levels. It has no drops other than bones, however, and is not in a prime location compared to other giant rats' locations.
